OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777510993
OL,3,CUniversity wins High Court challenge
OL,4,Cagainst regulator over free speech
OL,5,Cpenalty
OL,7,FThe University of Sussex has won a
OL,8,FHigh Court challenge against England's
OL,9,Fhigher education regulator over a
OL,10,Ffinding that it had infringed on
OL,11,Flawful free speech.
OL,13,FThe university took legal action
OL,14,Fagainst the Office for Students (OfS)
OL,15,Flast year over the watchdog's decision
OL,16,Fin March 2025 that the university had
OL,17,Fbreached conditions of registration
OL,18,Fthrough its trans and non-binary
OL,19,Fequality policy statement.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
