PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777510993
OL,3,CUniversity wins High Court challenge
OL,4,Cagainst regulator over free speech
OL,5,Cpenalty
OL,7,FThe decision came after a more than
OL,8,Fthree-year investigation following
OL,9,Fstudent protests related to the gender-
OL,10,Fcritical views of former staff member
OL,11,FProfessor Kathleen Stock.
OL,13,FShe resigned after the protests in
OL,14,Fresponse to her views in 2021, with
OL,15,Fthe OfS finding the university's
OL,16,Fpolicy had "a chilling effect" of
OL,17,Fpossible self-censorship of students
OL,18,Fand staff on campus.
OL,26,@xD@LOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
