OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777510993
OL,3,CUniversity wins High Court challenge
OL,4,Cagainst regulator over free speech
OL,5,Cpenalty
OL,7,FThe OfS found the policy breached
OL,8,Fregistration conditions and that the
OL,9,Funiversity had not acted in accordance
OL,10,Fwith its internal rules for adopting
OL,11,Fpolicies, handing it a record #585,000
OL,12,Ffine.
OL,14,FThe university, which has more than
OL,15,F19,000 students, challenged the
OL,16,Fregulator's decision at the High
OL,17,FCourt, telling a hearing in February
OL,18,Fthat the OfS's decision had "severe"
OL,19,Fconsequences for the institution and
OL,20,Fon its reputation as a "bastion of
OL,21,Ffree speech".
OL,26,@zD@]OUzD@dO]|D@XOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
