PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777510993
OL,3,CUniversity wins High Court challenge
OL,4,Cagainst regulator over free speech
OL,5,Cpenalty
OL,7,FThe OfS defended the claim, telling
OL,8,Fthe court the investigation was
OL,9,F"careful and detailed" and "pursuant
OL,10,Fto a fair procedure".
OL,12,FIn a judgment on Wednesday, Mrs
OL,13,FJustice Lieven ruled in the
OL,14,Funiversity's favour, finding the OfS
OL,15,F"misdirected itself".
OL,17,FShe also said the regulator's decision
OL,18,Fwas "vitiated by bias" as it
OL,19,Fapproached the decision "with a closed
OL,20,Fmind and had therefore unlawfully
OL,21,Fpredetermined the decision".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@VO]qD@\OUrD@TO]wD@AOUwD@TO]zD@
OL,26,AEOUzD@VO]{D@YOU}D@[O]
