PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777510993
OL,3,CUniversity wins High Court challenge
OL,4,Cagainst regulator over free speech
OL,5,Cpenalty
OL,7,FThe judge said the legal challenge did
OL,8,Fnot concern "any of the issues or
OL,9,Ffacts surrounding what happened to
OL,10,FProfessor Stock", but instead "is
OL,11,Fconcerned with whether the OfS erred
OL,12,Fin law, either in respect of its
OL,13,Fjurisdiction, its interpretation of
OL,14,Fthe law, or the lawfulness of its
OL,15,Fprocess".
OL,26,@pD@MOUrD@PO]rD@_OUwD@HO]
